cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with robust estimation in computer vision, which suggests that cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The use of graph-cut algorithm and RANSAC also suggests that cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics) are possible categories. The paper also introduces a novel method for estimation, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
